room_title: Escape room "Zombie Outbreak: The Cure" by Encryption in Maryville
room_description:
The zombie virus is quickly spreading and the government is frantically trying to get it under control. In an effort to try and find a cure, laboratories have been opened, stocked full with the walking dead and commanded by mad scientists at the helm. But zombies are not easily controlled, and they escaped taking the researchers with them. The cure was nearly completed when they fell victim to the very creatures they were trying to help. 
You've been tasked with completing the cure before you join the fate of your predecessors. Can you complete the cure in time? Or will you fail to save humanity from this horrible virus.
